Linus and Luke dive into the RTX 5060 series launch, calling out NVIDIA for what they believe was a consumer-unfriendly rollout of the new GPUs. Linus also shares why LTT chose not to publish a full review, and how the LTT Labs team is improving its internal processes for future GPU launches.
